OL,3,CFreeview technical change means 4Seven
OL,4,Cis now universally available
OL,6,GJust when you think the writing is on
OL,7,Gthe wall for Freeview a surprise pops
OL,8,Gup.
OL,10,FEngineering changes mean Channel 4 has
OL,11,Fbeen able to squeeze 4Seven on to its
OL,12,Fgifted space on one of the public
OL,13,Fservice multiplexes.
OL,15,FPreviously this channel was carried on
OL,16,Fcommercial capacity hired by C4.
OL,18,FThe new arrangement saves C4 money and
OL,19,Fmeans 4Seven is now universally
OL,20,Favailable.
