OL,6,FIf C4 were to shut this channel in the
OL,7,Ffuture, it could potentially use the
OL,8,Fspace for another service like Film4 +
OL,9,F1.
OL,11,FThe latest move represents yet another
OL,12,Fpiecemeal improvement to the so-called
OL,13,FFreeview Light service.
OL,15,FGradually a greater number of ITV and
OL,16,FC4's spin-off channels have become
OL,17,Funiversally available.
OL,19,FIt is possible that further technical
OL,20,Fimprovements could lead to more of
OL,21,Ftheir + 1 services becoming
OL,22,Funiversally available in the future.
