OL,3,CFreeview technical change means 4Seven
OL,4,Cis now universally available
OL,6,FTurning off Freeview is only viable
OL,7,Fwhen only a small proportion of
OL,8,Fcustomers rely on it.
OL,10,FDo not read too much into the recent
OL,11,Fdecision to turn off a tiny relay
OL,12,Ftransmitter in rural Scotland.
OL,14,FThis transmitter served a tiny number
OL,15,Fof viewers and was affected by a
OL,16,Fnearby wind farm.
OL,18,FAny decision to switch off a
OL,19,Ftransmitter should be taken on a case-
OL,20,Fby-case basis.
