OL,6,FI have argued before that some tiny
OL,7,Frelay transmitters ` originally built
OL,8,Fto deal with analogue problems or
OL,9,Fserve tiny communities ` may no longer
OL,10,Fbe needed in practice. But that's a
OL,11,Fdifferent issue to Freeview as a whole.
OL,13,FDo not underestimate how important it
OL,14,Fis for public service broadcasters to
OL,15,Fmaintain what might seem like outdated
OL,16,Fdistribution platforms to help support
OL,17,Fthe vulnerable.
OL,19,FYet again, there is still no confirmed
OL,20,Fdate for the end of Radio 4 Long Wave.
