OL,6,FThe teleswitching service for
OL,7,Felectricity meters will start to be
OL,8,Fturned off from 30th June. We can say
OL,9,Fconfidently now that R4 LW won't go on
OL,10,Fthis date.
OL,12,FAll this 15 years after shutting off
OL,13,FR4 LW was first seriously proposed by
OL,14,Fthe BBC and more than a year after
OL,15,Fseparate LW programming ended.
OL,17,FNew technology does not always mean
OL,18,Fthe end is nigh.
